      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/558570350_18525111460056563_5929858868762658448_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=MzczNDYzOTM1ODMxNDg2MDM4MA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=8roTcxAgykUQ7kNvwH8_BPo&amp;_nc_oc=AdpF54NDXYZIqs9xnzd2SieG4FUM-0VMyMGUGLi4qlDd3Ky4DitzNZmTGJYATXW5aIg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=nT6Aum08bDRuHY_uJ6Xflg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afyo7ejQxQIs0QdkcilgwUFCAkfpAUpSJ_DaCFTvSPrCJw&amp;oe=69C95918" alt="Instagram billede fra @manifest.raw" /></p><p><strong>@manifest.raw</strong></p><p>Last saturday Manifest celebrated 30 years of misbehaving responsibly, that’s a little over my entire life span, and I’m forever happy to be a part of the fresh energy in my only 5 years in the crew 🖤 - I wouldn’t have wanted to be anywhere else in the world - cheers to 30 more, and many more pictures coming 🫶🏻 @manifest_cph<br/>
