      <title>Backstage moment with @pennyvalent 🔥 Approaching people, with a camera after the...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DMqOdsUI8cn/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/525397074_18512809996056563_3519308663855087584_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=MzY4NjgyMjg1ODA1NDY4MjQwNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=TKxNPC61im8Q7kNvwHI5-h2&amp;_nc_oc=AdpfQ858Mp3kpqFF5TSz3INj8_MoBIMEwiM-8Z6anJUakXsRRZjoglJivWMpOZVuBEI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=nT6Aum08bDRuHY_uJ6Xflg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyHVGWbq29DhGka-wHsJIoqiAVah-qCk8twTRnuK8yfUg&amp;oe=69C977A5" alt="Instagram billede fra @manifest.raw" /></p><p><strong>@manifest.raw</strong></p><p>Backstage moment with @pennyvalent 🔥<br/>
<br/>
Approaching people, with a camera after their performance at events can sometimes be a bit…. scary - and feel like you’re invading peoples personal recharge space, but a kind approach turned out to be the most casual and comfy 15 minutes chilling and chatting at @manifest_cph 🖤<br/>
<br/>
Cheers to the backstage - Cheers to @pennyvalent and your great performance 🖤</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/525397074_18512809996056563_3519308663855087584_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=MzY4NjgyMjg1ODA1NDY4MjQwNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=TKxNPC61im8Q7kNvwHI5-h2&amp;_nc_oc=AdpfQ858Mp3kpqFF5TSz3INj8_MoBIMEwiM-8Z6anJUakXsRRZjoglJivWMpOZVuBEI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=nT6Aum08bDRuHY_uJ6Xflg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyHVGWbq29DhGka-wHsJIoqiAVah-qCk8twTRnuK8yfUg&amp;oe=69C977A5" alt="Instagram billede fra @manifest.raw" /></p><p><strong>@manifest.raw</strong></p><p>Backstage moment with @pennyvalent 🔥<br/>
<br/>
Approaching people, with a camera after their performance at events can sometimes be a bit…. scary - and feel like you’re invading peoples personal recharge space, but a kind approach turned out to be the most casual and comfy 15 minutes chilling and chatting at @manifest_cph 🖤<br/>
<br/>
Cheers to the backstage - Cheers to @pennyvalent and your great performance 🖤</p>]]></content:encoded>
